name: THE TICKLE - Issue #37
description:
Art zine focused on Tezos NFT artists and creative writers.

Issue #37 is a photography focused edition, curated by Lina Irem Arditty ( @arditty ) and co-curators Damla Sahinbas ( @damlasahinbas_ ) & Roman Drits ( @romandrits ).

Featured this week are artists Silvia Maria ( @silviahmariah ), Katya Kanke ( @katyakanke ) & Bárbara Bezina ( @BarbaraBezina ), with astrological writing by Karissa Tesluk Piszko ( @astroviak )

Created by artists Wily Guys ( @guyswily ) & Theo Horsmeier ( @THorsmeier ) and writer Joanne Rush ( @JonicolaRush ).
